<A>__{grabs the first thing he lays eyes on, a tiny snail fork and plunges it into barbosa's neck. as if it were a fly bite, barbosa flings the table aside and, with a long knife already in his hand, guts eddie from groin to breast bone. eddie falls like a suddenly emptied sack. elias can't help gasping. hull looks away, hiding his horror. barbosa rips the fork out of his neck and hurls it at the body.}
